data.description: Welcome home to a piece of paradise! This colonial sits at the end of a private cul-de-sac on over half an acre in the sought after Rexwood developement atop the hill in Glen Rock and close to the community park.  Be amazed from the moment you step foot in the door with the 2 story foyer, hardwood floors and beautiful decor.  As you pass the dining room to your left step down into the sunken living/family room with new flooring, a wall of windows and a floor to ceiling fireplace. The kitchen boasts quartz counter tops, large island and a serene sunroom and eating area overlooking the fenced in heated salt water pool just off the trex deck and paver patio.  Outside you will also find two separate fish ponds and a spot behind the pool for horseshoes. Back inside and upstairs feel the comfort of new carpet through out as you stroll through the 4 bedrooms , 3 with huge walk in closets and the 4th bedroom with 2 closets.  As a convenient bonus find the hidden laundry chute in the hallway closet.  In the Master bedroom awaits a soaker tub for those chilly evenings, a dual vanity, a stand up shower and ceramic tile. Top things off with a covered porch for some front porch sittin' and a glass of lemonade.
